<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Clarence" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Clarence,</orth> 1) Lionel Duke of C., son of Edward III: <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.4.83" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 4, 83</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.5.75" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 5, 75</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.2.13" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 2, 13</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.2.145" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 145</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.4.29" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 29</bibl>. -- 2) Thomas of C., son of Henry IV: <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.4.16" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 4, 16</bibl> etc. <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.84" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 2, 84</bibl>. -- 3) George of C., son of Richard of York and brother to Edward IV and Richard III: <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.6.104" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 6, 104</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.3.208" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 208</bibl> etc. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.1.34" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 1, 34</bibl> etc. etc.<lb />Gen. <cit><quote>Clarence':</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.2.145" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 2, 145</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.4.29" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 29</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.4.191" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 4, 191</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 2.1.136" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 136</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.1.144" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 144</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 55</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>